Version 1beta2 - released 2013-01-17
cmb     modified to keep scroll position after polling when not scrolled down to the bottom (inspired by stoa and snafu)
cmb     added possibility to display date and time of postings (suggested by snafu and stoa)
cmb     removed underscore from allowed characters of a chat room to avoid ambiguities
cmb     changed intervall_poll to be measured in seconds instead of milliseconds
cmb     improved user manual
cmb     added German localization and user manual
cmb     added Czech and Slovak localization (contributed by oldnema resp. Tata)
cmb     modernized styling
cmb     removed jQuery dependency
cmb     refactored several parts of the code

Version 1beta1 - released 2012-02-05
cmb	initial release
